                  <persName id="t18281023-25-person242">
                  ELIZA 
                  CUTBUSH
               <interp inst="t18281023-25-person242" type="surname" value="CUTBUSH"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18281023-25-person242" type="given" value="ELIZA"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18281023-25-person242" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I live in New Church-street, Edgware-road - there is a canal near my house; the deceased was four years old - he was missing for some time, and at last his body was found in the canal: the prisoner is eight years and a half old - I had some conversation with him, before the body was found; I was anxious to know where it was, and told him nothing should happen to him, if he told the truth.</p>
               <p>
            
